CM_ BO_ 2566836222 "Emission-Related Pending Diagnostic Trouble Codes. The purpose of this DM is to enable the external test equipment to obtain pending diagnostic trouble codes. The definition of a pending DTC varies according to the applicable regulatory guidance. Some regulations define pending to be a DTC detected during current or last completed driving cycle for emission-related components/systems";
