CM_ SG_ 2566836222 RedStopLampStatus "This lamp is uesed to relay trouble code information that is of a severe enought condition that it warrants stopping the vehicle.";
CM_ SG_ 2566836222 AmberWarningLampStatus "This lamp is used to relay trouble code information that is reporting a problem with the vehicle system but the vehicle need
