CM_ BO_ 2566835966 "Diagnostic Readiness 1. This message reports the diagnostics information that relates to diagnostic readiness";
CM_ SG_ 2566835966 OBDCompliance "Identifies the OBD compliance capabilityof the responding controller.";
CM_ SG_ 2566835966 PreviouslyActiveTroubleCodeCount "Identifies the number of previously active trouble codes that are present in a specific controller.";
CM_ SG_ 2566835966 ActiveTroubleCodeCount "Identifies the number of active trouble codes that are present in a specific controller.";
CM_ BO_ 2566835710 "Freeze Frame Parameters. This message is defined as the list of recorded parameters at the time a diagnostic trouble code was captured. The freeze frame recorded for each diagnostic trouble code will contain the required parameters first, and then any manufacturer-specific information";
CM_ SG_ 2566835710 EngIntakeManifold1Press "The gage pressure measurement of the air intake manifold.";
CM_ SG_ 2566835710 FreezeFrameLength "The freeze frame length shall be equal to the number of bytes in the required parameters plus the number of bytes in the
manufacturer specific parameters.";
CM_ SG_ 2566835710 EngSpeed "Actual engine speed which is calculated over a minimum crankshaft angle of 720 degrees divided by the number of cylinders.";
CM_ SG_ 2566835710 EngTorqueMode "State signal which indicates which engine torque mode is currently generating, limiting, or controlling the torque.";
CM_ SG_ 2566835710 WheelBasedVehicleSpeed "Speed of the vehicle as calculated from wheel or tailshaft speed.";
CM_ SG_ 2566835710 EngPercentLoadAtCurrentSpeed "The ratio of actual engine percent torque (indicated) to maximum indicated torque available at the current engine speed,";
